Research seminar in social pharmacy is prepared for students writing final paper connected with social pharmacy subjects. During seminars the following points will be studied: connections between social pharmacy and sociology, psychology and economics, drug communication, drug legislation of Estonia and European Union.Objectives/eesmärkid:  During particular seminar student can learn mean principles in social pharmacy studies and questions concerning his/her final paper in detail.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  During particular seminar student can learn mean principles in social pharmacy studies and questions concerning his/her final paper in detail. After completing the course, student is familiar with the requirements of the research work. Student has composed a research plan in co-operation with supervisor and has worked through the respective scientific literature.
